{"tid":2370850,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「學生動源」4人去年涉國安法被捕　其中3人今獲警主動交還護照","createTime":"2021-01-18T10:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T02:11:46.000Z","uid":6497,"like":25,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"36bfa96347f539c93e12d20bd6caf31430902f00","tid":2370850,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:21:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210118/s00001/1610956815726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210118%2Fs00001%2F1610956815726&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=5b275399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210118%2Fs00001%2F1610956815726&h=fbc89d2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210118/s00001/1610956815726</a><br />\n<br />\n去年宣布解散香港分部的「學生動源」，其前召集人鍾翰林、前成員何忻諾、陳渭賢及何諾恆，先後於去年7月底及10月被警方國安處兩度拘捕，其中鍾翰林已被落案起訴及正被還押，另外3人當時獲准保釋及需交出護照。至今日（18日），何諾恆、何忻諾及陳渭賢獲警方主動交還護照，何諾恆稱一直認為自己被起訴機率低，警方交還護照令3人暫時放下心頭大石。本報正向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何諾恆表示，數天前接獲警方來電，要求他今日到其報到的警署辦理手續，但沒有透露詳情，僅稱並非落案起訴。他今午到田心警署，負責的警員主動交還其護照及保釋金，稱會暫時釋放他，惟稱由於案件仍在調查，其手機、電腦等財物仍未可交還。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據何諾恆了解，警方去年7月向法庭申請扣留4人護照半年，限期將至前警方沒有向法庭申請續期。何忻諾及陳渭賢亦於今日獲交還護照，何諾恆相信警方「冇料到」。雖然目前獲交還護照，何諾恆亦認為自己被起訴的機率甚低，但不能排除日後再被羅織其他罪名，目前短暫放下心頭大石後仍要繼續過日常生活。"},{"pid":"0d32aa0dcd527bd5f6ce334bf3fb8a0bf8d41d4c","tid":2370850,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:29:47.000Z","msg":"高調咬人"},{"pid":"d51a92f2af9f8efec155accc335b25ee0240a39b","tid":2370850,"uid":147941,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"拎返護照快d走"},{"pid":"016ab4b1dd50a18474050c580c42a290cf0dbb71","tid":2370850,"uid":385809,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"即走啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入得佢個 &quot;黑名單&quot;，遲到一日又咬過"},{"pid":"95d02626c07650bb8c424e3bb8643ca622947ca4","tid":2370850,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"016ab4b1dd50a18474050c580c42a290cf0dbb71","tid":2370850,"uid":385809,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:31:23.000Z","msg":"即走啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入得佢個 &quot;黑名單&quot;，遲到一日又咬過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:32:20.000Z","msg":"唔駛講啦呢樣"},{"pid":"b025759c124c37f8db4e6ed9495927219b7d6801","tid":2370850,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:33:06.000Z","msg":"留喺到死路一條"},{"pid":"a2a1a52f67aba8f7536acf99b61f2bcae69d4e70","tid":2370850,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"竟然還PASSPORT? 有冇咁好死?"},{"pid":"1ff72a894f183aebc7db473b89302459531ca3c1","tid":2370850,"uid":6497,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2a1a52f67aba8f7536acf99b61f2bcae69d4e70","tid":2370850,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"竟然還PASSPORT? 有冇咁好死?"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"證明冇料到兼覺得佢地冇威脅"},{"pid":"0598ad50fcb309ffac937b9ffe6e8f86704e59b2","tid":2370850,"uid":90521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"囉到護照就好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2842b1ae94d7b28974fd83608355aa6371079f8e","tid":2370850,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:36:30.000Z","msg":"好走，老實"},{"pid":"c55c4c9dea42c8e7867adae8a30d75ad3eabcbd4","tid":2370850,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"希望佢地走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf0780b48abcd7af2b55f1aada843cbf1c24b69","tid":2370850,"ui